---
// Meet the Blitz mascot section
---

<section class="py-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-orange-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
            <!-- Mascot Image -->
            <div class="flex justify-center lg:justify-start">
                <div class="relative">
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-400 to-orange-400 rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-30"></div>
                    <img
                        src="/images/mascot.jpg"
                        alt="MouldBlitz Superhero Mascot"
                        class="relative w-80 h-80 object-cover rounded-full shadow-2xl border-8 border-white transform hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300"
                    />
                    <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 bg-orange-500 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-bold text-lg shadow-xl rotate-12 animate-bounce">
                        Your Hero!
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Content -->
            <div>
                <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-6">
                    Meet <span class="text-blue-600">The Blitz</span>
                </h2>
                <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
                    Our superhero mascot represents what we do best: <span class="font-bold text-orange-600">striking mould with lightning speed</span> and eliminating it for good!
                </p>
                <div class="space-y-4">
                    <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 shadow-md">
                            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                                <path d="M11 3a1 1 0 10-2 0v1a1 1 0 102 0V3zM15.657 5.757a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414l-.707.707a1 1 0 001.414 1.414l.707-.707zM18 10a1 1 0 01-1 1h-1a1 1 0 110-2h1a1 1 0 011 1zM5.05 6.464A1 1 0 106.464 5.05l-.707-.707a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l.707.707zM5 10a1 1 0 01-1 1H3a1 1 0 110-2h1a1 1 0 011 1zM8 16v-1h4v1a2 2 0 11-4 0zM12 14c.015-.34.208-.646.477-.859a4 4 0 10-4.954 0c.27.213.462.519.476.859h4.002z"/>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-gray-900 mb-1">Lightning-Fast Service</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600">Just like our superhero, we move fast! 48-hour response times and same-day quotes.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-orange-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 shadow-md">
                            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M6.267 3.455a3.066 3.066 0 001.745-.723 3.066 3.066 0 013.976 0 3.066 3.066 0 001.745.723 3.066 3.066 0 012.812 2.812c.051.643.304 1.254.723 1.745a3.066 3.066 0 010 3.976 3.066 3.066 0 00-.723 1.745 3.066 3.066 0 01-2.812 2.812 3.066 3.066 0 00-1.745.723 3.066 3.066 0 01-3.976 0 3.066 3.066 0 00-1.745-.723 3.066 3.066 0 01-2.812-2.812 3.066 3.066 0 00-.723-1.745 3.066 3.066 0 010-3.976 3.066 3.066 0 00.723-1.745 3.066 3.066 0 012.812-2.812zm7.44 5.252a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-gray-900 mb-1">Powerful Results</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600">We don't just mask the problemâ€”we eliminate mould at the source with our proven methods.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 shadow-md">
                            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M2.166 4.999A11.954 11.954 0 0010 1.944 11.954 11.954 0 0017.834 5c.11.65.166 1.32.166 2.001 0 5.225-3.34 9.67-8 11.317C5.34 16.67 2 12.225 2 7c0-.682.057-1.35.166-2.001zm11.541 3.708a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-gray-900 mb-1">Protected & Guaranteed</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600">90-day mould-free guarantee. Your home stays protected, or we return free!</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
